25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aeschin.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.25</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παρὰ τετάρτην ἡμέραν ἑκάστῃ σημαίᾳ καθήκειν τὴν λειτουργίαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:33:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.33.9</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Cair.Zen.:218:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PCair.Zen.\">PCair.Zen.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">218.24</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B.C.)</date>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῆς βολῆς καθηκούσης ἐς αὐτόν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg015:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Alc.\">Alc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐν τῷ ξυμποσίῳ . . ἐπὶ τὸν Θεσμόπολιν καθῆκε τὸ σκῶμμα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg033:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Merc.Cond.\">Merc.Cond.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">34</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n51792.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of Time, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁπότε καθήκοι ὁ Χρόνος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:7:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href